For the tuna patties, place all the patty ingredients into the bowl of a food-processor and blend until the mixture is well combined.Roll the patty mixture into four patties. Heat the olive oil in a small frying pan and fry for three minutes each side or until golden-brown.For the cucumber relish, place all the relish ingredients into a clean medium-sized bowl and mix well to combine.To serve, place the patties on a clean plate and serve with the cucumber relish in a small bowl on the side.